\c 55
\s Dhavhidhi anochema pakutambudzika kwake kukuru, asi anovimba naJehovha
\d Kumutungamiriri wokuimba; nemitengeramwa. Rwiyo rweMashiri rwaDhavhidhi.
\p
\v 1 Rerekerai nzeve yenyu kumunyengetero wangu, Mwari; regai kuzvivanza pakukumbira kwangu.
\v 2 Nditeererei, mundipindure. Ndinodzungaira mukuchema kwangu, ndichivuvura.
\v 3 Nokuda kwenzwi romuvengi, nokuda kokumanikidza kowakaipa; nokuti vanondipomera zvakaipa, vanonditambudza nokutsamwa kwavo.
\v 4 Moyo wangu unorwadziwa kwazvo mukati mangu; garudzo rorufu rakandiwira.
\v 5 Kutya nokubvunda zvakandiwira. Kutya kukuru kwakandifukidza.
\v 6 Ini ndakati: Haiwa, dai ndaiva namapapiro senjiva! Ndaibhururuka, ndikanozorora.
\v 7 Tarirai, ndingadai ndaitizira kure, ndaindogara kurenje.
\v 8 Ndaikurumidza kundovanda, nditize mhepo inovhuvhuta nedutu guru.
\p
\v 9 Paradzai, Ishe mukanganise marimi avo; nokuti ndakaona kumanikidza nokurwa muguta.
\v 10 Masikati novusiku vanoripoteredza pamasvingo aro; zvakaipawo nezvakashata zviri mukati maro.
\v 11 Kushata kuri pakati paro; kumanikidza nokunyengera hazvibvi panzira dzaro.
\v 12 Nokuti akange asi muvengi akandishora; ipapo ndaigona kutsunga; akange asi iye aindivenga akazvikudza kwandiri; ipapo ndaimuvanda.
\v 13 Asi wakange uriwe, munhu wakaenzana neni, shamwari yangu, nomuzikamwi wangu.
\v 14 Taisirangana zvakanaka, taifamba mumba maMwari pamwe chete navanhu vazhinji.
\p
\v 15 Rufu ngaruvawire kamwe-kamwe, ngavaburikire kuSheori vari vapenyu, nokuti kushata kuri paugaro hwavo, imo mukati mavo.
\v 16 Kana ndirini, ndichadana kuna Mwari; Jehovha achandiponesa.
\v 17 Madekwani namangwanani namasikati ndichachema ndichivuvura; iye achanzwa inzwi rangu.
\v 18 Wakadzikunura mweya wangu nerugare, kukasava neumwe akaswedera kwandiri, nokuti vakange vachirwa neni, vaiva vazhinji.
\v 19 Mwari achanzwa, achavapindura, iye aripo kare nakare. Nokuti havashanduki, havatyi Mwari.
\v 20 Wakatambanudzira maoko ake kuna vaiva norugare naye; wakashora sungano yake.
\v 21 Mashoko omuromo wake akatedza samafuta, asi kurwa kwakange kuri pamoyo pake; mashoko ake akange ari manyoro kupfuura mafuta, kunyange zvakadaro yaiva minondo yakavhomorwa.
\p
\v 22 Kandira mutoro wako pamusoro paJehovha, iye achakusimbisa; haangatongotenderi akarurama kuti azununguswe.
\v 23 Asi imwi Mwari muchavaburusira kugomba rokuparadzwa; vanhu vanokarira ropa navanonyengera havangapedzi hafu yamazuva avo; asi ini ndichavimba nemi.
